{"tid":667692,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保方姐姐：他還沒決定要退役 誰說40就不能踢了","createTime":"2018-05-17T03:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T05:13:59.000Z","uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1afbceb182f8634109652cb9f9afc1b9d8504b0","tid":667692,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"根據《拖連奴體育報》報導，祖記門將保方的姐姐維羅妮卡-保方表示，她不認為自己的弟弟即將退役。<br />\n<br />\n　　「我在球場上看到他越多，就越不覺得他將會走向陽光（指退役去渡假）。」維羅妮卡對《拖連奴體育報》說。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n<br />\n　　「我曾是排球運動員，當我27歲時，我有1000個理由可以退役，但是我很好奇吉吉會怎麼做？就因為他40歲了嗎？這又怎麼樣呢？我們討論的是一位幫助祖記奪得聯賽7連冠，並且連續4次奪得意大利盃冠軍的門將。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「更不用提歐冠盃了，在班拿貝，他貢獻了精彩的表現，吉吉是聯合國教科文組織級別的世界寶物（heritage），請相信我，我也曾從事高水平的運動。我是他的姐姐，我非常愛她，我對他有偏愛，但是我不認為他到說再見（指退役）的時候，他的眼神沒有給我想要停下來的感覺。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我曾跟他談過很多次，但是吉吉是個好人，他就笑著，一直回答道：&lsquo;也許這樣更好吧。&rsquo;作為他的姐姐，以及前運動員，我想要聽到他說：&lsquo;我要停下了，因為我不再擁有它了。&rsquo;但是現在並不是這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n　　談到2006年祖記被降入意乙聯賽時，維羅妮卡表示：「我們都很茫然失措，一起討論祖記降班的事情，我望著吉吉，問他：&lsquo;你下季要去哪裡。&rsquo;」<br />\n<br />\n　　「他被我嚇到了，他說：&lsquo;我會留下，哪怕是在那裡。&rsquo;當時我覺得他瘋了，但是就我對他的瞭解，這並不意外，這就是我的弟弟，一個依感情用事的簡單小夥。他給體育總監阿列西奧-塞科同樣的答案，我能向你保證，作為世界冠軍，他本可以去任何地方踢球。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我的弟弟一直給祖記和意大利隊貢獻一切，因此當我聽到過去2場意大利友誼賽，人們對他的爭議性言論，我很失望。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">比我就插住喉都踢啦 屌你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"bcb913df7dbb8e9a1a0652afb27e3cca37b68a9d","tid":667692,"uid":44584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:18:07.000Z","msg":"永續保方<br />\n關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7b675f6453603082d580d9f92120b157bde970","tid":667692,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"支持保方下屆世界盃正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f8e981dc76a76e0dd26ef1b326d8ee0912d867","tid":667692,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db7b675f6453603082d580d9f92120b157bde970","tid":667692,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"支持保方下屆世界盃正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"踢到當拿隆馬個代退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137fa82d52b3a6d6ea7e52369cb7450e39d464b8","tid":667692,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31f8e981dc76a76e0dd26ef1b326d8ee0912d867","tid":667692,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db7b675f6453603082d580d9f92120b157bde970","tid":667692,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"支持保方下屆世界盃正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"踢到當拿隆馬個代退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"祖記意甲20連霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d556cd2dc5cde2ad9127b74231eb35655f9a2cc3","tid":667692,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"137fa82d52b3a6d6ea7e52369cb7450e39d464b8","tid":667692,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31f8e981dc76a76e0dd26ef1b326d8ee0912d867","tid":667692,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db7b675f6453603082d580d9f92120b157bde970","tid":667692,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,